Date: 1993-09-09

Title: Abelian Chern-Simons theory as the strong large-mass limit of

Authors: G. Giavarini, C.P. Martin and F. Ruiz Ruiz

Comments: phyzzx, 17 pages, FTUAM 93/27, UPRF 93/376 and NIKHEF-H 93/17 (to

appear in Nucl. Phys. B)Journal-ref: Nucl. Phys. B412 (1994) 731

We show that the renormalized vacuum expectation value of the Wilson loop fortopologically massive abelian gauge theory in $\RR^3$ can be defined so thatits large-mass limit be the renormalized vacuum expectation value of the Wilsonloop for abelian Chern-Simons theory also in $\RR^3$.